dat1<- filter(mydata,Year==2019)[,c(2,3)]
head(dat1)
dat1$month <- as.integer(strftime(dat1$发布时间, '%m')) # 月份
dat1$monthf<-factor(dat1$month,levels=as.character(1:12),
labels=c("Jan","Feb","Mar","Apr","May","Jun","Jul","Aug","Sep","Oct","Nov","Dec"),ordered=TRUE)
dat1$weekday<-as.integer(strftime(dat1$发布时间, '%u'))# 周数
dat1$weekdayf<-factor(dat1$weekday,levels=(1:7),
labels=(c("Mon","Tue","Wed","Thu","Fri","Sat","Sun")),ordered=TRUE)
dat1$yearmonth<- strftime(dat1$发布时间, '%m%Y') # 月份
dat1$yearmonthf<-factor(dat1$yearmonth)
dat1$week<-as.integer(strftime(dat1$发布时间, '%W'))# 周数
dat1<-dat1 %>%
    group_by(monthf)%>%
    mutate(monthweek=1+week-min(week))
dat1$day<-strftime(dat1$发布时间, "%d")
dat1
ggplot(dat1, aes(weekdayf, monthweek, fill=总播放数)) +
geom_tile(colour = "white") +
scale_fill_gradientn(colours=rev(brewer.pal(11,'Spectral')))+
geom_text(aes(label=day),size=3)+
facet_wrap(~monthf ,nrow=3) +
scale_y_reverse()+
xlab("Day") + ylab("Week of the month") +
theme(strip.text = element_text(size=11,face="plain",color="black"))
